  "description": [
    "PAGE 10 East Hartford Conn Gazette THURSDAY APRIL 5 1962 In District I Daniel Neil Is New Kelley March is the month for cele brations at the Gagliardi house hold Mr and Mrs Rocco Gag liardi of Woodbridge Ave cele brated their 27th anniversary on the 22nd hey have two daughters Roccine and Kose Marie and two grandsons Mrs Gagliardi also had a birthday on the 25th A family gath ering was held and a good time was had by all Daniel G Murphy of Burn FREE MON TUES J SPARKLING RINSE BY CLAIROL With a wash and set at our regular low price MARGES SALON 665 BURNSIDE AVE EH BU 95145 PERSONAL To Whom It May Concern If the person or persons that have been telling me right along that the 1962 Chevrolet line is the most fabulous car line ever offered would please come forward I would like to thank them for their good advice I have wasted hours and hours looking at the new 62s but they were right The Chevy line has them all beat Now maybe I can give all of you a tip Dworin Chevrolet at 476 Conn Boulevard East Hartford is the place"
  ],
